metadata.name: Money Rune
metadata.description:
This fast rune stav for all occasions brings very ckopo results: it starts its work a couple of days after activation, and in particularly difficult cases - no longer than two weeks.
 The runes included in it and their work : 

Teivaz - destroys all obstacles that prevent the entry of finance into your life
 
Algiz - protects all your cash receipts 

Effzet - directs a person to "money" places
 
Dagaz - promotes the discovery of new sources of goxoga 

Mannaz - denotes the person for whom the bet works 

Four Inguz - symbolize the arrival of wealth 

Two Lags - make the cash flow constant

for activating the runes, write in a personal account
